{
  "stem": "58.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my uncle got killed in the first flour mill.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His name was Ishmuel Schultz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they bombed the city at random, just to make chaos, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The first thing they did is take out 12 Jews that belonged to the city government and the elder, they shot him in the middle, in the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was the first [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] taste of the German brutality.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then a lot of us escaped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were in, actually four kilometers in our orchards that we were gathering the fruit for the fall already.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Germans came in-- we heard the news about what happened in the city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I, actually I was always the one that took the initiative.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I went into the city, and I saw what's going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The next day they came in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they parked the tanks under the trees.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were still fighting for Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one-- a day or two after they parked the tanks under the trees in the orchards, they, they were pushed back from Warsaw by the Polish defenders a few kilometers.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So they picked up men, from 15 to 50, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] picked me up and my father.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they took us to the city jail, kept us overnight.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You know rumors were going around that maybe they'll mine the, the jail or whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Next morning, they marched us out, six wide, about 3,500 people, Poles and Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They marched us with-- in a dirt road, to a city, Biala, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] without water, without food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "If you run for a little water that people used to hand out, you were shot.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
